The paper deals with the achievable rate region for the cognitive radio channel, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). It also involves networked systems (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY) as it deals with the transmission of information over a network and the use of decoding techniques. Finally, the paper specifically focuses on the cognitive radio channel (cs.CR), which is a subfield of communication and networking.
